Name: CrunchTime
About the game: A long-term crunch time programmer entered the world of code, and became a green cursor. Knowing that the condition for getting off work is to find 4 bugs in the code world, the adventure begins... Classic platformer style The world of ASCII, full of old-school flavor Well-designed levels and boss battles Collect emails from your boss and experience the mood of crunch time programmers Developed by several former long-term crunch time programmers (with ❤).
